</span><span style="color:#bbb"> </span>- .gitlab-ci.yml <span style="color:#bbb"> </span><span style="color:#228b22"># CI/CD</span><span style="color:#bbb">
</span></code></pre></div><h2 id="2project-下各个gradle文件">2、Project 下各个gradle文件</h2>
